{
  "stem": "26142.11",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came to Satu Mare and to that hotel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we asked for the-- they were the owners of that hotel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we got over there, we found out that her father, which was my mother's uncle, was one of the 17, 19 people that was left in Torun, that he left Torun.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That he-- his daughter that owned the hotel took him away and told him, you have nothing to, to, to stay there anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he stayed with her in the hotel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They gave him a room in the hotel there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we got in there, they put us into this room where, where this Uncle [INAUDIBLE] was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, he started asking about his granddaughter and his family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the same thing again, we, we, we, we told him, we don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But anyway, he was able to contact-- now I don't know how they contacted-- the two uncles-- and he was able to contact them I think with a messenger because I don't think they have telephones-- to come over.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they came over, they were very surprised to see us, see us over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this grand uncle of ours, he said, here are Abraham [INAUDIBLE] two children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You are two uncles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You divide among ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You take one, and you take one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And of course, they, they agreed and it felt-- My older brother Tsvi kind of felt that I would-- I would feel-- I would feel more comfortable to stay with my mother's brother, with the Darvas family because they were more modern and, and not so [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the other were [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he knew that I wouldn't feel too well anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He sized up the situation pretty well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so we got divided up.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
